    "excerpt": "A group reading of Megilat Esther arranged by Naomi Klionsky at Bezalel (Chicago), Thursday, 13 March 2025. Each character in the megillah is read by a reader cast for that voice. ",
    "content": "<p>A group reading of Megilat Esther arranged by Naomi Klionsky at <a href=\"https://www.timesofisrael.com/chicago-couple-transforms-rundown-former-synagogue-into-shared-community-space/\">Bezalel</a> (Chicago), Thursday, 13 March 2025. Each character in the megillah is read by a reader cast for that voice.<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> This idea dates to Purim in 2015 (subsequently shared via a social media post) where at a family reading by Aharon Varady and his parents each listener took responsibility for reading the voice of a set of characters.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> The recording was made by Naomi Klionsky in one unbroken take. (The resulting digital file was then divided into chapters by Aharon Varady without any added audio effects.)</p>\n<p>Chapter 1<br />\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-0-1\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2001%20-%20Chapter%201.mp3?_=1\" /><a href=\"https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2001%20-%20Chapter%201.mp3\">https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2001%20-%20Chapter%201.mp3</a></audio></p>\n<p>Chapter 2<br />\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-0-2\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2002%20-%20Chapter%202.mp3?_=2\" /><a href=\"https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2002%20-%20Chapter%202.mp3\">https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2002%20-%20Chapter%202.mp3</a></audio></p>\n<p>Chapter 3<br />\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-0-3\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2003%20-%20Chapter%203.mp3?_=3\" /><a href=\"https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2003%20-%20Chapter%203.mp3\">https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2003%20-%20Chapter%203.mp3</a></audio></p>\n<p>Chapter 4<br />\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-0-4\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2004%20-%20Chapter%204.mp3?_=4\" /><a href=\"https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2004%20-%20Chapter%204.mp3\">https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2004%20-%20Chapter%204.mp3</a></audio></p>\n<p>Chapter 5<br />\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-0-5\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2005%20-%20Chapter%205.mp3?_=5\" /><a href=\"https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2005%20-%20Chapter%205.mp3\">https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2005%20-%20Chapter%205.mp3</a></audio></p>\n<p>Chapter 6<br />\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-0-6\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2006%20-%20Chapter%206.mp3?_=6\" /><a href=\"https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2006%20-%20Chapter%206.mp3\">https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2006%20-%20Chapter%206.mp3</a></audio></p>\n<p>Chapter 7<br />\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-0-7\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2007%20-%20Chapter%207.mp3?_=7\" /><a href=\"https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2007%20-%20Chapter%207.mp3\">https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2007%20-%20Chapter%207.mp3</a></audio></p>\n<p>Chapter 8<br />\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-0-8\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2008%20-%20Chapter%208.mp3?_=8\" /><a href=\"https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2008%20-%20Chapter%208.mp3\">https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2008%20-%20Chapter%208.mp3</a></audio></p>\n<p>Chapter 9<br />\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-0-9\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2009%20-%20Chapter%209.mp3?_=9\" /><a href=\"https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2009%20-%20Chapter%209.mp3\">https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2009%20-%20Chapter%209.mp3</a></audio></p>\n<p>Chapter 10<br />\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-0-10\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2010%20-%20Chapter%2010.mp3?_=10\" /><a href=\"https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2010%20-%20Chapter%2010.mp3\">https://archive.org/download/naomi-klionsky-and-friends-megilat-esther-2025/Naomi%20Klionsky%20%26%20friends%20-%20Megilat%20Esther%20-%2010%20-%20Chapter%2010.mp3</a></audio></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"speaker-mute footnotes_reference_container\"> <div class=\"footnote_container_prepare\"><p><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_label pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_expand_collapse_reference_container__1();\">Notes</span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button\" style=\"display: none;; display: none;\" onclick=\"footnote_expand_collapse_reference_container__1();\"></span></p></div> <div id=\"footnote_references_container__1\" style=\"\"><table class=\"footnotes_table footnote-reference-container\"><caption class=\"accessibility\">Notes</caption> <tbody> \r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >1</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">This idea dates to Purim in 2015 (subsequently shared via a social media post) where at a family reading by Aharon Varady and his parents each listener took responsibility for reading the voice of a set of characters.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n </tbody> </table> </div></div><script type=\"text/javascript\"> function footnote_expand_reference_container__1() { jQuery('#footnote_references_container__1').show(); jQuery('#footnote_reference_container_collapse_button__1').text('−'); } function footnote_collapse_reference_container__1() { jQuery('#footnote_references_container__1').hide(); jQuery('#footnote_refe